It would not work against 2.6.5, since
do_syscall_trace()
makes the check
if (!test_thread_flag(TIF_SYSCALL_TRACE))
		return;
Simply removing it would do?
On Tue, 2004-05-11 at 14:12, Davide Libenzi wrote:
